{"tid":2261240,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(梁天琦《地厚天高》導演) 林子穎拍攝網絡喜劇，已在網站播放。","createTime":"2020-10-28T07:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T14:49:47.000Z","uid":134071,"like":59,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"bc913d7f5d8c41612124ca6110a332535e761b4b","tid":2261240,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T07:13:06.000Z","msg":"獨立電影導演<strong>林子穎（Nora）</strong>早前與《蘋果動新聞》合作拍攝喜劇《星期日早上》，<strong>題材沒有如《地厚天高》般嚴肅，而是比較近似她執導的短片《全部都係雞》及《四段四分鐘》</strong>，都是探討兩性關係之餘，又打破一些傳統價值觀，Nora說：「算係摸索緊自己鍾意嘅創作方向，so far覺得拍喜劇係好玩嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n一按即睇 果燃台︱星期日早上<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3ma4CSD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3ma4CSD&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7D632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=60696d5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3ma4CSD</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201026/ZCPX56N3VREEJPYCMDJNHYP25M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201026%2FZCPX56N3VREEJPYCMDJNHYP25M%2F&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7D632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=5645034a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201026%2FZCPX56N3VREEJPYCMDJNHYP25M%2F&h=eb4d5875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201026/ZCPX56N3VREEJPYCMDJNHYP25M/</a>"},{"pid":"bed54fe26babcb9c83a8a991d81c9b91febbd2a3","tid":2261240,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T07:13:25.000Z","msg":"支持黃圈手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775c44d9fbe40d4bf2ee2252fb74bc21bbe7fbbb","tid":2261240,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T07:13:57.000Z","msg":"支持黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6db91ce56ba49858a1c1799da47024d4e77e0c6","tid":2261240,"uid":232157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTim